This situation really sparks feelings.

566
00:17:46,740 --> 00:17:48,180
But I think you can tell

567
00:17:48,180 --> 00:17:49,820
Zizheng is really going all out.

568
00:17:49,820 --> 00:17:51,500
(He's all in)
Exactly.

569
00:17:51,780 --> 00:17:52,140
I swear

570
00:17:52,140 --> 00:17:53,540
I'm dying to see it.

571
00:17:53,540 --> 00:17:55,100
Wish I could be Mr. Fantastic

572
00:17:55,500 --> 00:17:57,060
and stretch my arm right over.

573
00:17:57,460 --> 00:17:58,660
But I just can't reach.

574
00:17:58,820 --> 00:18:00,380
But this scene is so cool.

575
00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:01,420
Yeah.

576
00:18:01,420 --> 00:18:03,140
A destiny vibe.

577
00:18:03,140 --> 00:18:04,900
Exactly.

578
00:18:04,900 --> 00:18:06,620
(Fated script)
That's exactly it.

579
00:18:07,500 --> 00:18:09,900
When I felt the pull ease up behind me,

580
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:11,740
I knew my chance came.

581
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:12,660
Come on, Guanjie.

582
00:18:12,660 --> 00:18:13,900
Keep going, Guanjie!

583
00:18:22,900 --> 00:18:24,980
(Impressive)
He's so strategic.

584
00:18:27,870 --> 00:18:29,060
(Beyond hope)
Gave it his all.

585
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:30,300
That was already amazing.

586
00:18:30,300 --> 00:18:32,020
Yeah, I think he did great.

587
00:18:32,020 --> 00:18:32,820
Yeah.

588
00:18:33,300 --> 00:18:33,820
It's okay.

589
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:35,220
Let's have instant noodles.

590
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:39,100
Yijia's so sweet too.

591
00:18:39,100 --> 00:18:40,140
He didn't win,

592
00:18:40,140 --> 00:18:41,500
but he already got what he wanted.

593
00:18:41,500 --> 00:18:42,060
Right.

594
00:18:42,340 --> 00:18:44,060
Let's eat instant noodles.

595
00:18:45,820 --> 00:18:47,140
How about we add two eggs?

596
00:18:47,140 --> 00:18:48,020
Two fried eggs.

597
00:18:48,620 --> 00:18:50,620
(So sweet)
I really like Yijia's personality.

598
00:18:50,620 --> 00:18:51,820
Too sweet.

599
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:54,180
Feels just like
a real high school drama.

600
00:18:54,500 --> 00:18:57,380
(Best Campus Couple)

601
00:18:57,920 --> 00:18:59,180
(Round 2: Ye Jiajie VS Lu Yanting)
Go!

602
00:18:59,180 --> 00:19:00,260
(Swift strike)
Come on!

603
00:19:00,260 --> 00:19:01,180
(Caught off guard)

604
00:19:01,740 --> 00:19:02,860
That was intense.

605
00:19:02,860 --> 00:19:04,500
(First match begins)
His energy's not drained.

606
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:05,340
Yeah.

607
00:19:05,340 --> 00:19:06,700
Makes sense.

608
00:19:06,700 --> 00:19:09,140
Keep going!

609
00:19:09,140 --> 00:19:10,900
Almost there.

610
00:19:14,140 --> 00:19:16,340
Jie's down to the sand already.

611
00:19:16,340 --> 00:19:18,020
(Busy eating sand, don't disturb)

612
00:19:19,060 --> 00:19:20,060
For Jiayi!

613
00:19:20,060 --> 00:19:21,500
Come on!

614
00:19:21,500 --> 00:19:22,340
You're close enough.

615
00:19:22,340 --> 00:19:22,940
One step left.

616
00:19:22,940 --> 00:19:23,620
Hurry.

617
00:19:23,620 --> 00:19:24,540
Pull harder.

618
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:26,700
(Nervous)

619
00:19:26,780 --> 00:19:28,060
Just a tiny bit more.

620
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:29,020
Go!

621
00:19:34,980 --> 00:19:36,500
That's impressive.

622
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:38,780
(Hard-earned win)
He's totally that (man).

623
00:19:39,260 --> 00:19:40,740
(Final: Wu Guanjie VS Lu Yanting)
No mercy.

624
00:19:40,740 --> 00:19:42,740
Got it?

625
00:19:42,740 --> 00:19:44,020
You have to take her to eat.

626
00:19:44,020 --> 00:19:45,020
He's cheering Yanting on

627
00:19:45,020 --> 00:19:46,500
so that Guanjie and Yan

628
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:48,380
won't end up going to Black Pearl.

629
00:19:48,380 --> 00:19:50,580
That's his own secret plan.

630
00:19:51,100 --> 00:19:52,980
(My happiness is on you, bro)

631
00:19:53,060 --> 00:19:54,820
After several exhausting rounds,

632
00:19:54,820 --> 00:19:57,140
I didn't expect Guanjie
to still be so strong.

633
00:19:57,140 --> 00:19:59,020
I was just being dragged along
at the end.

634
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:01,100
Keep going!

635
00:20:01,260 --> 00:20:03,620
Go, Guanjie!

636
00:20:08,780 --> 00:20:10,380
Guanjie's Guan means Champion.

637
00:20:10,380 --> 00:20:10,900
But seriously

638
00:20:10,900 --> 00:20:11,540
he's already strong

639
00:20:11,540 --> 00:20:12,900
and he eats well, super nourished.

640
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:13,900
So he's getting even better.

641
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:17,260
(In tip-top shape)
He hasn't had a bad meal since he got here.

642
00:20:17,260 --> 00:20:18,420
Yeah.

643
00:20:21,140 --> 00:20:23,020
Is that really true?

644
00:20:23,300 --> 00:20:24,260
Just watch them eat?

645
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:25,620
That's bad.

646
00:20:26,100 --> 00:20:27,980
(Bitter smile)

647
00:20:28,180 --> 00:20:29,820
How's Jiawei

648
00:20:29,820 --> 00:20:30,500
feeling right now?

649
00:20:30,980 --> 00:20:33,300
So sad, tears of sorrow.

650
00:20:33,300 --> 00:20:34,620
I think he'll let it go gradually.

651
00:20:34,620 --> 00:20:35,420
Actually.

652
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:38,100
Because I think he clearly feels that

653
00:20:38,100 --> 00:20:40,780
Zhu Huiyan has a huge crush on Guanjie.

654
00:20:40,780 --> 00:20:41,300
Yeah.

655
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:50,060
Do you think Jiawei

656
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:51,860
will go talk to Huiyan again?

657
00:20:51,860 --> 00:20:53,900
If it were you, would you?

658
00:20:54,980 --> 00:20:56,980
I don't think I'd talk to her again.

659
00:20:56,980 --> 00:20:57,940
Because I think

660
00:20:57,940 --> 00:20:59,220
this girl has clearly shown

661
00:20:59,220 --> 00:21:01,140
she has a big crush

662
00:21:01,140 --> 00:21:02,460
on another guy.

663
00:21:02,460 --> 00:21:03,380
For me,

664
00:21:03,380 --> 00:21:03,900
basically,

665
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:05,620
she has no crush at all.

666
00:21:05,620 --> 00:21:06,140
(Laughing)

667
00:21:06,140 --> 00:21:07,180
(What's wrong?)
So maybe,

668
00:21:07,180 --> 00:21:08,500
from my point of view,

669
00:21:08,500 --> 00:21:11,220
I won't ask for embarrassment anymore.

670
00:21:11,220 --> 00:21:13,900
Maybe he'll talk to her one last time
to make things clear.

671
00:21:13,900 --> 00:21:15,540
And get a definite answer.

672
00:21:15,540 --> 00:21:17,500
Then maybe everything will make sense.

673
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:18,100
I guess.

674
00:21:18,100 --> 00:21:19,660
(Could be possible)
Maybe Huiyan

675
00:21:19,660 --> 00:21:21,860
needs to say one last thing to him

676
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:23,340
to make him let go completely.

677
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:24,300
Yeah.

678
00:21:24,300 --> 00:21:24,980
So actually I think

679
00:21:24,980 --> 00:21:27,180
fate is such a magical thing.

680
00:21:27,180 --> 00:21:28,460
These two just hit it off.

681
00:21:28,460 --> 00:21:30,860
(Timing can't beat the depth of fate)
But nothing came of it.

682
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:32,340
Now his situation has become

683
00:21:32,340 --> 00:21:33,300
pretty awkward.

684
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:34,820
If he had met someone else first.

685
00:21:34,820 --> 00:21:38,020
Fate's just so magical.

686
00:21:38,020 --> 00:21:38,980
Let me interrupt.

687
00:21:38,980 --> 00:21:40,940
This is a souvenir

688
00:21:40,940 --> 00:21:41,980
prepared for today.

689
00:21:41,980 --> 00:21:43,260
Once you open it,

690
00:21:43,260 --> 00:21:44,860
you can

691
00:21:44,860 --> 00:21:47,940
write a short note
to each other right now,

692
00:21:47,940 --> 00:21:49,780
or draw a little doodle.

693
00:21:50,620 --> 00:21:51,820
Looking forward to this.

694
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:53,780
I'm really curious too.

695
00:21:55,060 --> 00:21:55,980
I'm really curious

696
00:21:56,860 --> 00:21:57,660
about what it'll be.

697
00:21:58,620 --> 00:21:59,620
Just a random sketch.

698
00:22:01,980 --> 00:22:02,780
(What?)

699
00:22:02,860 --> 00:22:03,860
I drew a table

700
00:22:03,860 --> 00:22:05,180
to document life.

701
00:22:06,860 --> 00:22:07,460
A random sketch

702
00:22:07,580 --> 00:22:09,100
(That casual?)
A random sketch?

703
00:22:09,100 --> 00:22:09,780
Exchanging cards

704
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:10,820
is actually supposed to be

705
00:22:10,820 --> 00:22:12,060
a pretty serious moment.

706
00:22:12,060 --> 00:22:13,700
You said you wanna document life.

707
00:22:14,540 --> 00:22:15,700
Drew two little dots.

708
00:22:15,700 --> 00:22:16,380
Yeah.

709
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:18,460
(That's interesting)

710
00:22:18,940 --> 00:22:20,060
Done talking yet?

711
00:22:20,060 --> 00:22:20,660
We're done.

712
00:22:20,660 --> 00:22:21,220
Yeah.

713
00:22:21,220 --> 00:22:21,580
What about?

714
00:22:21,580 --> 00:22:23,300
Okay, I'll borrow a bit of her time.

715
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:25,220
(Guess it right)
They talked after all.

716
00:22:25,540 --> 00:22:26,500
Honestly, I really

717
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:29,700
admire Huang Jiawei here.

718
00:22:29,700 --> 00:22:30,300
(Impressed)
Yeah.

719
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:31,540
Still had the courage to talk.

720
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:32,980
Because I went all in yesterday.

721
00:22:34,340 --> 00:22:35,060
Yeah, but…

722
00:22:35,500 --> 00:22:36,140
You tell me

723
00:22:36,900 --> 00:22:37,620
you didn't.

724
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:39,260
Now I'm telling you again,

725
00:22:39,260 --> 00:22:40,580
but I can't explain it clearly.

726
00:22:40,580 --> 00:22:41,980
Honestly, I don't know how to say it.

727
00:22:41,980 --> 00:22:42,940
With Guanjie's appearance,

728
00:22:42,940 --> 00:22:44,820
I lean more towards Guanjie.

729
00:22:44,820 --> 00:22:45,580
But anyway,

730
00:22:45,580 --> 00:22:46,060
I'll

731
00:22:46,320 --> 00:22:47,940
respect your thoughts and your decision.

732
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:48,980
Yeah.

733
00:22:49,180 --> 00:22:50,340
Respect my thoughts,

734
00:22:51,020 --> 00:22:52,140
and I'll respect yours.

735
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:54,220
(Pointless)
This chat changed nothing.

736
00:22:54,220 --> 00:22:55,180
Right.

737
00:22:55,180 --> 00:22:55,860
A fail.

738
00:22:56,020 --> 00:22:57,300
Mainly this girl's attitude

739
00:22:57,300 --> 00:22:59,060
dooms this talk to nothing.

740
00:22:59,060 --> 00:23:00,220
Yeah.

741
00:23:00,900 --> 00:23:01,860
Hello.

742
00:23:01,860 --> 00:23:02,300
Jiayi.

743
00:23:02,300 --> 00:23:03,900
Why are you sitting here alone?

744
00:23:03,900 --> 00:23:05,380
Honestly, a bit regretful.

745
00:23:05,380 --> 00:23:06,500
At the first day...

746
00:23:06,500 --> 00:23:07,860
Why didn't you say anything?

747
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:08,820
Maybe it's

748
00:23:08,820 --> 00:23:10,020
because of our different backgrounds.

749
00:23:10,020 --> 00:23:11,780
And maybe I

750
00:23:11,780 --> 00:23:14,140
take things a bit slower

751
00:23:14,140 --> 00:23:15,100
when pursuing someone.

752
00:23:15,100 --> 00:23:15,500
I think...

753
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:19,100
What do you think about his

754
00:23:19,100 --> 00:23:19,900
sudden confession?

755
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:22,740
I think it has a lot to do with
his personality.

756
00:23:22,740 --> 00:23:23,740
His personality

757
00:23:23,740 --> 00:23:25,700
is actually a bit of a disadvantage

758
00:23:25,700 --> 00:23:27,340
in this survival setting.

759
00:23:27,340 --> 00:23:30,620
Because he's not very proactive.

760
00:23:30,620 --> 00:23:31,580
And also, you know.

761
00:23:31,580 --> 00:23:33,660
(Passive)
Sometimes he doesn't mind giving in.

762
00:23:33,660 --> 00:23:34,140
Yeah.

763
00:23:34,140 --> 00:23:38,100
I think he's the one

764
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:40,940
with the least drama
among all the male guests.

765
00:23:41,180 --> 00:23:42,020
What's that?

766
00:23:43,860 --> 00:23:44,420
Take a guess.

767
00:23:44,700 --> 00:23:46,020
A bouquet.

768
00:23:46,020 --> 00:23:47,020
Wildflowers.

769
00:23:47,700 --> 00:23:49,220
(Wildflowers)

770
00:23:51,380 --> 00:23:52,340
You're spot on.

771
00:23:52,780 --> 00:23:54,220
You even matched it so well.

772
00:23:54,820 --> 00:23:56,260
It's pretty. Where'd you get?

773
00:23:56,260 --> 00:23:57,180
Where's this from?

774
00:23:57,550 --> 00:23:58,620
His emotional value for Jiayi

775
00:23:58,620 --> 00:23:59,940
(Maxed out emotional value)
is off the charts.

776
00:23:59,940 --> 00:24:01,780
But this really touched me.

777
00:24:01,780 --> 00:24:02,980
I love this.

778
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:06,500
Because I remembered her saying

779
00:24:06,500 --> 00:24:08,100
she likes flowers last night.

780
00:24:08,980 --> 00:24:11,260
(Yesterday: Lu Yanting and Liu Jiayi's date)
Flowers are nice.

781
00:24:11,260 --> 00:24:12,860
And if she genuinely loves flowers.

782
00:24:12,860 --> 00:24:13,980
He made a bouquet like this.

783
00:24:13,980 --> 00:24:15,020
A meaningful one just for her.

784
00:24:15,020 --> 00:24:16,540
(Nailed her fancy)
I think it touched her.

785
00:24:16,540 --> 00:24:17,980
This is promising.

786
00:24:17,980 --> 00:24:19,940
I'm starting to ship them again.

787
00:24:23,660 --> 00:24:24,940
An indoor date?

788
00:24:24,980 --> 00:24:27,380
(Jealous)

789
00:24:27,540 --> 00:24:30,540
Feels like this will be everyone's
favorite scene.

790
00:24:31,500 --> 00:24:33,420
Attention, islanders.

791
00:24:33,420 --> 00:24:35,500
New islanders are about to arrive.

792
00:24:36,860 --> 00:24:38,820
There's more?

793
00:24:43,100 --> 00:24:43,740
So handsome.

794
00:24:45,140 --> 00:24:46,100
Wow, that's so cool.

795
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:48,100
New islander arriving tonight

796
00:24:48,100 --> 00:24:50,540
will replace the original islander.

797
00:24:54,700 --> 00:24:55,700
Show me the next episode.

798
00:24:56,150 --> 00:24:57,900
(Still wanting more)
How is it already over?

799
00:24:57,980 --> 00:24:59,500
(Q: Who do you think
will leave next episode?)

800
00:24:59,500 --> 00:25:02,500
Jiaming and Yihan are a little risky.

801
00:25:02,500 --> 00:25:04,420
Jiaming and Huang Jiawei also

802
00:25:04,420 --> 00:25:05,820
don't have anyone

803
00:25:05,820 --> 00:25:07,540
who clearly likes them right now.

804
00:25:07,540 --> 00:25:09,860
(Male guest Xuan Cheng is at risk)
Xuan Cheng's situation seems shaky.

805
00:25:09,860 --> 00:25:12,380
Because no one clearly
wants to vote for him.

806
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:13,460
I think it's Xuan Cheng too.

807
00:25:13,900 --> 00:25:15,580
I think after Jiawei talked

808
00:25:15,580 --> 00:25:16,580
with Huiyan,

809
00:25:16,580 --> 00:25:17,220
he clearly

810
00:25:17,220 --> 00:25:19,300
realized she won't vote all for him.

811
00:25:19,300 --> 00:25:20,940
But if that's the case,

812
00:25:20,940 --> 00:25:22,460
Huiyan might not even

813
00:25:22,460 --> 00:25:23,700
(At risk)
get all the votes.

814
00:25:23,860 --> 00:25:25,860
I don't think
Guanjie will vote all for her.

815
00:25:25,860 --> 00:25:26,220
Right.

816
00:25:26,220 --> 00:25:29,300
I think Jiawei
might give Huiyan two votes.

817
00:25:29,300 --> 00:25:30,900
(2 votes, 1 vote)
and one to Jiaming.

818
00:25:30,900 --> 00:25:33,180
(The final stubbornness)
His final bit of stubbornness.

819
00:25:33,820 --> 00:25:34,660
This is tough.

820
00:25:35,420 --> 00:25:36,860
(Q: Which CP do you ship the most?)
Zizheng and Yijia.

821
00:25:36,860 --> 00:25:38,100
We're die-hard shippers.

822
00:25:38,100 --> 00:25:38,500
Yeah.

823
00:25:38,500 --> 00:25:40,420
I ship them the most.

824
00:25:40,420 --> 00:25:43,740
(Sweet Couple)
So sweet it makes you believe in love again.

825
00:25:43,740 --> 00:25:45,300
I feel like Jiayi…

826
00:25:45,300 --> 00:25:48,060
I don't ship her
with Xuan Cheng anymore.

827
00:25:48,060 --> 00:25:50,580
I think Jiayi's a very proactive girl

828
00:25:50,580 --> 00:25:52,380
and if she really had a crush on someone

829
00:25:52,380 --> 00:25:54,060
right now,

830
00:25:54,060 --> 00:25:55,620
she'd totally make the first move.

831
00:25:55,620 --> 00:25:57,740
So I think none of these three guys

832
00:25:57,740 --> 00:25:59,140
have really caught her eye right now.

833
00:25:59,580 --> 00:26:03,180
(Mysterious new guest)
Let's look forward to our new guest.

834
00:26:03,180 --> 00:26:04,420
Thanks for watching

835
00:26:04,420 --> 00:26:06,220
"Watch Live and Love S2 With Us",

836
00:26:06,220 --> 00:26:07,580
Episode 3.

837
00:26:07,580 --> 00:26:10,660
There are still so many mysteries
waiting for us.

838
00:26:12,940 --> 00:26:14,740
Hurry and tell us.

839
00:26:16,780 --> 00:26:33,740
("Live and Love" Release Schedule)

840
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:36,420
(Watch Live and Love with us)
♪Take a look at my girlfriend♪

841
00:26:36,600 --> 00:26:38,410
(on Thurs. at 12 pm.)
♪She's the only one I got♪

842
00:26:38,410 --> 00:26:40,080
♪Ba ba da da♪

843
00:26:40,290 --> 00:26:42,680
♪Not much of a partner♪

844
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:44,550
♪I never seem to get much♪

